{"id":490,"date":"2022-12-19T02:29:04","date_gmt":"2022-12-19T02:29:04","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gaviaspreview.com\/wp\/gowilds\/?page_id=23"},"modified":"2026-01-15T03:53:44","modified_gmt":"2026-01-15T03:53:44","slug":"about","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.royalstarexpeditions.com\/about\/","title":{"rendered":"About"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"490\" class=\"elementor elementor-490\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-ee503c8 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"ee503c8\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;slideshow&quot;,&quot;background_slideshow_gallery&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:673,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https:\\\/\\\/www.new.northblockscivilworks.co.ke\\\/wp-content\\\/uploads\\\/2026\\\/01\\\/watamu-1.jpg&quot;},{&quot;id&quot;:669,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https:\\\/\\\/www.new.northblockscivilworks.co.ke\\\/wp-content\\\/uploads\\\/2026\\\/01\\\/MARA-1.jpg&quot;},{&quot;id&quot;:675,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https:\\\/\\\/www.new.northblockscivilworks.co.ke\\\/wp-content\\\/uploads\\\/2026\\\/01\\\/watamu-3-1.jpg&quot;}],&quot;background_slideshow_ken_burns&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;background_slideshow_transition_duration&quot;:800,&quot;background_slideshow_loop&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;background_slideshow_slide_duration&quot;:5000,&quot;background_slideshow_slide_transition&quot;:&quot;fade&quot;,&quot;background_slideshow_ken_burns_zoom_direction&quot;:&quot;in&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-8028c45\" data-id=\"8028c45\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-44fce45 elementor-widget elementor-widget-gva-heading-block\" data-id=\"44fce45\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"gva-heading-block.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"gva-element-gva-heading-block gva-element\">   <div class=\"align-center style-1 widget gsc-heading box-align-left auto-responsive\">\r\n      <div class=\"content-inner\">\r\n         \r\n                  \r\n           \r\n         \r\n                     <h2 class=\"title\">\r\n               <span>About Us<\/span>\r\n            <\/h2>\r\n                  \r\n         \r\n         \r\n      <\/div>\r\n   <\/div>\r\n<\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-1b4968e elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"1b4968e\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-e65d88c\" data-id=\"e65d88c\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8d2ca6e elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8d2ca6e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Royal Star Expeditions\n<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7587e3f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7587e3f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>With vacation packages to Kenya, Uganda, Tanzania, and Zanzibar, Royal Star Expeditions stands out as one of the most reputable indigenously owned Tours &amp; Safari Companies in Kenya. It is a fully licensed safari and tour operator based in Nairobi, Kenya, with its headquarters there. We are also represented on\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.safaribookings.com\/\">SafariBookings.com<\/a>.\u00a0<\/p><p>Royal Star Expeditions\u00a0can help you organize the perfect honeymoon, a daring East African adventure holiday, the ultimate Kenya, Uganda, and Tanzania safari, or a memorable family vacation. Royal Star Expeditions\u00a0is dedicated to providing you with unforgettable African safaris, ecotourism, and adventure travel experiences.<\/p><p>All of our itineraries are tailored to give you a taste of African culture, modern lifestyle, and wildlife. We do, however, customize our journeys to our clients\u2019 preferences, so no two experiences are ever the same.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-06a4c45\" data-id=\"06a4c45\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b907891 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"b907891\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" src=\"https:\/\/www.royalstarexpeditions.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/ROYAL-1024x683.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-685\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.royalstarexpeditions.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/ROYAL-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.royalstarexpeditions.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/ROYAL-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.royalstarexpeditions.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/ROYAL-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.royalstarexpeditions.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/ROYAL.jpg 1800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-5bfd331 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"5bfd331\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-1b9b658\" data-id=\"1b9b658\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-76aee5e\" data-id=\"76aee5e\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b2efcbf elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"b2efcbf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">What Makes us Different\n<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b8f83a6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b8f83a6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"gdlr-core-pbf-element\"><div class=\"gdlr-core-text-box-item gdlr-core-item-pdlr gdlr-core-item-pdb gdlr-core-left-align\"><div class=\"gdlr-core-text-box-item-content\"><p>Due to our expertise and knowledge of the wildlife history and habitat, as well as the supply of Safaris Holiday planning and Ground handling services by online and abroad Travel Agents, we have become one of the most sought-after Safari and Tour Operators in East Africa.<\/p><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"gdlr-core-pbf-element\"><div class=\"gdlr-core-text-box-item gdlr-core-item-pdlr gdlr-core-item-pdb gdlr-core-left-align\"><div class=\"gdlr-core-text-box-item-content\"><p>The huge lodges packed with tourists are not for you if you want to experience the authentic essence of Kenya, Uganda, Tanzania, or Zanzibar. We are here to give you huge, distant, exclusive, and exclusive concessions that cater to a small number of visitors, in collaboration with only the best of our local Kenyan partners. The mystical mood is unlike anything you are likely to ever encounter, with so few guests in such wide unspoilt swaths of wilderness.<\/p><p>Whatever your special interest, we have something that will meet your needs. We do all the research, plan your itinerary, provide necessary information and cover all details \u2013 all you need to do is pack your bag and prepare for the African vacation of a lifetime<\/p><\/div><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-9630cc9 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"9630cc9\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-de7a585\" data-id=\"de7a585\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a7df5d3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"a7df5d3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5a8b46c elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"5a8b46c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">About Services\n<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7da7776 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"7da7776\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-93ea47b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"93ea47b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"gdlr-core-pbf-element\"><div class=\"gdlr-core-text-box-item gdlr-core-item-pdlr gdlr-core-item-pdb gdlr-core-left-align\"><div class=\"gdlr-core-text-box-item-content\"><p>Throughout Kenya, Tanzania, and Uganda, our clients benefit from our trustworthy connections. This means that we will handle all of your holiday planning and ground handling logistics, including meet and greet formalities, assistance at the airport and hotel upon arrival, transfers to the respective hotels, accommodation arrangements and bookings, Tours and Safari organizations, conferences, and Group incentives to any East African destination of your choice.<\/p><p>In summary, we provide relevant expert advice and guidance on each inquiry and assist in the final product\u2019s coordination.<\/p><\/div><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-64ede19 elementor-align-center elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"64ede19\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"https:\/\/www.new.northblockscivilworks.co.ke\/?page_id=495\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Get A Quote<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-5e71cad\" data-id=\"5e71cad\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ae5c5dc elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"ae5c5dc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Royal Star Expeditions\n<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d9fcb45 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d9fcb45\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"gdlr-core-pbf-element\"><div class=\"gdlr-core-text-box-item gdlr-core-item-pdlr gdlr-core-item-pdb gdlr-core-left-align\"><div class=\"gdlr-core-text-box-item-content\"><p>Our culture of putting the customer first, teamwork and on time service delivery has played a key role in our success. We evaluate our clients\u2019 needs and then create tailor-made solutions whilst allowing room for future growth and expansion, in line with the rapidly changing face of the global Travel Industry.<\/p><p>Our long term experience of working closely with a wide range of clients and facing various kinds of scenarios has given us a unique balance of skills between knowing what is out there in terms of our clients\u2019 needs and understanding our market to make sure that our products are not only plausible but also possible and affordable.<\/p><p>Our client portfolios include Missionary groups, Research Student organizations, corporate incentive organizers, Conference organizers, Non Governmental organizations and online individual inquirers.<\/p><\/div><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>About Us Royal Star Expeditions With vacation packages to Kenya, Uganda, Tanzania, and Zanzibar, Royal Star Expeditions stands out as one of the most reputable indigenously owned Tours &amp; Safari [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_joinchat":[],"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-490","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.royalstarexpeditions.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/490","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.royalstarexpeditions.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.royalstarexpeditions.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.royalstarexpeditions.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.royalstarexpeditions.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=490"}],"version-history":[{"count":15,"href":"https:\/\/www.royalstarexpeditions.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/490\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":701,"href":"https:\/\/www.royalstarexpeditions.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/490\/revisions\/701"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.royalstarexpeditions.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=490"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w